OL,6,FShe received a sentence of six months'
OL,7,Fimprisonment, suspended for two years.
OL,9,FThe case is being sent to the Court of
OL,10,FAppeal posthumously following an
OL,11,Fapplication by Mrs Owen's family after
OL,12,Fshe died in 2003.
