OL,6,FMrs Owen's legal team stood down an
OL,7,Findependent IT specialist on the day
OL,8,Fof her trial despite Adrian Montagu's
OL,9,Freport concluding that "bugs and
OL,10,Ferrors existed in sufficiently
OL,11,Fsignificant numbers and seriousness"
OL,12,Fand that any evidence relying on the
OL,13,Fsystem "must be regarded as very
OL,14,Funsafe".
OL,16,FThe CCRC said in March that it was
OL,17,Fexamining 27 cases to determine
OL,18,Fwhether the Capture accounting
OL,19,Fsoftware played a part in convictions.
