OL,4,CCapture referred to Court of Appeal
OL,6,FThe Capture system pre-dated the now
OL,7,Finfamous Horizon software ` which has
OL,8,Fbeen responsible for almost 1,000
OL,9,Fwrongful convictions.
OL,11,FAn independent report into Capture was
OL,12,Fcommissioned last year after
OL,13,Fsubpostmasters said they had suffered
OL,14,Fsimilar problems to those faced by the
OL,15,FHorizon victims.
OL,17,FThe CCRC said it has sent more than 70
OL,18,Fcases associated with the Post Office
OL,19,FHorizon scandal to the appeal courts.
