OL,6,FSolicitor Neil Hudgell, whose firm
OL,7,FHudgell Solicitors represents more
OL,8,Fthan 100 people affected by the
OL,9,FCapture system, said the referral is a
OL,10,F"hugely positive step".
OL,12,FHe said: "This is another landmark
OL,13,Fmoment in the continuing campaign to
OL,14,Fensure all those who were wrongly
OL,15,Fprosecuted at the hands of the Post
OL,16,FOffice have their names cleared.
OL,18,F"Those who were affected by Capture
OL,19,Fhave suffered the longest of all.
