OL,6,F"However, this is a hugely positive
OL,7,Fstep, and we hope this is the first of
OL,8,Fmany cases to be referred for
OL,9,Fconsideration."
OL,11,FA Post Office spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"While it is not appropriate for us to
OL,13,Fcomment on specific cases, we have
OL,14,Fbeen very concerned about the reported
OL,15,Fproblems relating to the use of the
OL,16,FCapture software and we are sincerely
OL,17,Fsorry for past failings that have
OL,18,Fcaused suffering to postmasters.
